name: Sterling Silver & Freshwater Pearl Dangle Earrings
description:
Handwrought sterling silver earrings embossed with a subtle raised pattern and embellished with pretty little freshwater pearl dangles.  Earrings are a soft trapezoid shape and elegant exotic pattern is almost Moroccan in its aesthetic. Oxidized with a rich charcoal patina and steel brushed to a burnished glow, these contemporary urban metalsmith earrings are equally suitable with formal business attire or with a T-shirt and jeans.

Earrings measure 1" across at widest point and hang a total of 1 7/8" fro top of sterling silver ear wire to bottom of pearl dangles.

[E.698]

name: Large Round Hand-Stamped Artisan Hoop Earrings
description:
"Artisan Hoop" is the name I have given to a design that is a hybrid of a substantial metalsmith earring and a sideways-facing hoop, and which is textured identically on both sides so that there is no front side and no back side, allowing them to be worn in either ear and be visible from all angles.

This pair is forged and fabricated from substantial 22 gauge bronze and features a unique textural hand-stamped pattern which is shown to its best advantage with a rich dark patina and steel brushed finish.  A beautiful pair of contemporary urban metalwork earrings with an earthy, ethnic, tribal aesthetic.

Earrings are 1 3/4" in diameter and hang a total of 2 1/4" from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wires.

*The beautiful sheen of bronze can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[E.690]

name: Sterling Silver & Chrysophrase Drop Earrings
description:
Lovely feminine drop earrings crafted from sterling silver and gorgeous natural mint julep green faceted chrysophrase.  Modern contemporary urban gypsy dangle earrings are a hip and artsy take on the classic drop!

Earrings measure 3/8" at widest point and hang a total of 2 3/4" from top of forged, soldered sterling silver ear wire to bottom of teardrop.


[E.697]

name: Forged Bronze, African Bauxite & Indonesian Glass Organic Hoop Earrings
description:
Organic forged bronze hoop earrings embellished with primitive brick red African bauxite and multicolor striped Indonesian glass beaded dangles.  Rustic handwrought hoops are urban and stylish with a distinctly ethnic tribal vibe.

Large hoops measure just over 1 3/4" across and hang a total of approximately 2 5/8" from top of hypoallergenic titanium ear wire to bottom of beaded dangles.

*The beautiful sheen of bronze can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

To view complete photo albums of all my work visit https://www.facebook.com/pages/Lisa-Flanders-Studio/116857548332519?sk=photos_albums

[E.694]

name: Sterling Silver, Raw Amber, Raw Garnet & Turquoise Teardrop Dangle Earrings
description:
Long sterling silver dangle earrings crafted from hand forged and fabricated sterling teardrops embellished with gorgeous golden yellow raw amber, wine colored raw garnet, blue green turquoise and small agate accent beads that are the same shade as the amber. Metal has been given a rustic primitive texture and then oxidized and steel brushed to a rich charcoal patina which contrasts beautifully with the multicolored stones.

Earrings measure 5/8" across at widest point and hang a total of 3 7/8" from top of hypoallergenic titanium ear wires to bottom of dangles.

[E.683]

name: Wide Sterling Silver Cuff Bracelet
description:
Gorgeous 2" wide sterling silver cuff bracelet in one of my signature richly textural patterns. Cuff has been forged from substantial 20 gauge sterling sheet and metal has been oxidized and steel brushed to highlight unique handwrought pattern. Ultra-hip and stylish urban silver jewelry with a vibe that is exotic and ethnic and at the same time subtly industrial.

Bracelet is just over 6" in length and comes forged into a round shape, but is malleable enough to be gently formed to fit the wearer's individual wrist upon wearing.

name: Salvaged Antique Egyptian Brass & Carnelian Dangle Earrings
description:
Long exotic dangle earrings crafted from salvaged pieces of gorgeous antique Egyptian brass. These are cut from a larger fragment which featured Arabic script created with traditional metalwork techniques of repousse and chasing. They are then buffed smooth, oxidized and steel brushed, and embellished with a fringe of bright orange faceted carnelian dangles, each accented with a brass bead cap. Stunning stylish urban artisan statement earrings with a bohemian ethnic tribal gypsy flair.

Earrings measure just under 1 1/8" at widest point and hang a total of 2 3/4" from top of hypoallergenic titanium ear wire to bottom of dangles.

*The beautiful sheen of brass can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[E.684]

name: Titanium, Vintage Green Stone & Verdigris Brass Jeweled Hoop Earrings
description:
The latest pair of my signature jeweled hoops, these earrings feature handmade bronze colored titanium hoops embellished with brass disc dangles and earthy green stone beads salvaged from a vintage necklace.  The rustic look of the disc dangles was achieved by a 3-step process, in which I first applied a black patina, then rubbed some of it off and applied a blue green verdigris patina.  Finally, they were sealed with museum quality Renaissance Wax.  These stylish urban hoops have a distinctly primitive ethnic tribal boho vibe.

Titanium is a hypoallergenic, surgical implant grade metal and bronze color is achieved by anodizing.  Hoops measure 1 1/8" across (front to back) and hang a total of 1 5/8" from top of hoop to bottom of disc dangles.

[E.685]

name: Sterling Silver & Fossilized Bone Earrings
description:
Rustic, primitive earrings crafted from hand forged and fabricated organically textured sterling silver and gorgeous fossilized bone.  Beautiful and earthy in shades of brown, pale gray, charcoal gray and black.

Bone pieces were collected along the beaches of the Chesapeake Bay in southern Maryland, an area famous for its abundant fossils.

Earrings measure 3/8" at widest point and hang a total of 2 5/8" from top of ear wires.  Last photo shows a different pair of the same design to give a sense of what they look like on.  You will receive the pair shown in the first 4 photos.

[E.676]

name: Hammered Brass Hoop Earrings
description:
Super stylish large hammered brass hoop earrings.  Hand forged from a thick gauge of metal, these hoops have been given a classic hammered textured and then oxidized and steel brushed to a rich burnished glow.  These classic hoops fit any style and wardrobe, from clean, modern, contemporary and urban to an artsy boho gypsy look.

Narrow hoops measure 1/4" wide, just over 2" in diameter and hang a total of just under 2 3/8 from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wires.

[E.686]

name: Hammered Copper & Jasper Tribal Dangle Earrings
description:
In these stunning long dangle earrings, oxidized hammered copper shields hang from long handmade titanium ear wires that have been embellished with beautiful multi-hued green and rust brown jasper and long oxidized copper tubew.  Hand buffed blackened copper is stylish and sophisticated in these urban ethnic boho gypsy earrings.

Earrings measure 3/4" at widest point and hang a total of 2 3/4" from top of ear wire.

[E.681]

name: Vintage Black Clay Bird Earrings
description:
Lovely, earthy, spirited earrings crafted from vintage black clay birds on handmade sterling silver ear wires.  These beautiful vintage birds came from the estate of a world-traveling photographer, and I am reasonably certain they are traditional barro negro fired pottery, an ancestral craft of Oaxaca, Mexico.  

Birds are 3-dimensional and measure approximately 1" across and earrings hang a total of approximately 1" from top of forged sterling silver ear wires.  A drop of epoxy has been added inside the hole in order to secure the birds to the wire to keep them symmetrically facing in opposite directions and to prevent them from turning around.

These earrings will be made to order.  Please allow for slight variations, as all these birds are handmade and therefore slightly different.  All are equally beautiful.  Please allow 5 days fabrication time.

*Please note that the pair in the photos, which have sold, were the first pair of this design and I way overdid the epoxy, which is visible in these close-up photos.  As I perfect this technique, I will use less epoxy!

[E.669 MTO]

name: Sterling Silver, Raw Garnet & Antique Glass Dangle Earrings
description:
Part of my Return to the Elements series of primitive metalwork, these one of a kind dangle earrings are crafted from organic textural sterling silver, earthy wine colored raw garnet and rustic yellow green chartreuse antique glass.  Metal has been given a rich charcoal patina and then steel brushed to highlight handwrought texture.  Looking like some ancient artifact unearthed in an archaeological dig, these stylish urban earrings are wearable art for your ears.

Earrings measure 5/8" across at widest point and hang a total of 2 7/8" from top of graceful forged sterling silver ear wires to bottom of dangle.

[E.677]

name: Sterling Silver Hoop Earrings: Artisan Hoops I
description:
Large textural oval sterling silver hoop earrings in one of my signature deep handwrought textures. Fabricated from substantial 22 gauge sterling silver, metal is textured identically on both sides so that there is no front side or back side, allowing them to be worn in either ear and be visible from all angles. A bold, sophisticated, modern, contemporary urban design in classic silversmith earrings.

Earrings are approximately 1 1/8" wide x 1 3/4" long and hang a total of approximately 2 1/4" from top of surgical implant grade titanium ear wires.

*Please note that these earrings are not stamped sterling because I did not want to mar the texture, but they are sterling.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations. Please allow up to 3 days fabrication time.

name: Sterling Silver, Antique Glass & Jasper Dangle Earrings
description:
Stylish long earrings crafted from deeply textured sterling silver shield shaped pieces embellished with long stick dangles and gorgeous rustic primitive yellow green chartreuse antique glass and black-and-white jasper beads stacked on graceful forged sterling silver ear wires.  These modern contemporary urban earrings have a distinct ethnic, tribal, boho aesthetic.  

Earrings measure 3/4" across at widest point and hang a total of 3" from top of ear wire to bottom of stick dangle.

[E.678]

name: Sterling Silver Bangle Bracelet
description:
Hand forged and fabricated sterling silver bangle bracelet imprinted with a rustic primitive organic texture.  Bracelet is earthy and ancient looking, while at the same time having a contemporary urban, almost ever-so-slightly industrial vibe.  Metal has been oxidized and steel brushed to a rich charcoal patina to highlight handwrought texture.  Simple and striking worn alone or with other handmade silver jewelry.

Bangle is a slightly oval shape with a diameter of 2 1/2" in one direction and 2 3/4" in the other.  Will fit an average to large hand and wrist.

[B.5]

name: Lapis-in-Azurite, Indonesian Glass & African Brass Hand Dangle Earrings
description:
Earthy, richly colored ethnic earrings crafted from rustic African brass hands dangling beneath stylish long ear wires stacked with gorgeous blue green lapis-in-azurite and multicolor striped Indonesian glass beads.  

Detailed hands are hung so that they are symmetrical and opposite-facing.  Earrings measure 1/2" at widest point of hands and hang a total of 2 3/8" from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wire.

[E.692]

name: Sterling Silver & Apricot Moonstone Jeweled Dangle Earrings
description:
One of my signature designs, these jeweled dangle earrings feature richly textural sterling silver spear shaped pieces suspended beneath beautiful natural apricot moonstone cabochons.  Metal has been oxidized and steel brushed to highlight rustic primitive handwrought texture for a striking pair of contemporary urban earrings

Also known as peach moonstone, these cabochons are 6mm.  Earrings measure 3/8" across at widest point and hang a total of just under 2 3/4" from top of luxe sterling silver ear wires to bottom of spears.

[E.689]

name: Sterling Silver & Citrine Organic Spiral Earrings
description:
Part of my Return to the Elements series of primitive metalwork, these one of a kind dangle earrings are crafted from organic textural sterling silver spirals that have been embellished with beautiful bright sunny yellow citrine and sterling silver bicone dangles.  Metal has been given a rich charcoal patina and then steel brushed to highlight handwrought texture. Looking like some ancient artifact unearthed in an archaeological dig, these stylish urban earrings are wearable art for your ears.  

Earrings measure 1 1/8" across and hang a total of 2 3/8" from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wire to bottom of dangle.

[E.682]

name: Sterling Silver & Peridot Jeweled Dangle Earrings
description:
One of my signature designs, these jeweled dangle earrings feature richly textural sterling silver spear shaped pieces suspended beneath beautiful bright green peridot cabochons.  Metal has been oxidized and steel brushed to highlight rustic primitive handwrought texture for a striking pair of contemporary urban earrings.

Peridot cabochons are 6mm, and earrings measure 3/8" across at widest point and hang a total of 2 5/8" from top of luxe sterling silver ear wires to bottom of spears.

[E.688]

name: Raw Pyrite & Sterling Silver Drop Earrings
description:
An edgy, contemporary take on the classic drop, these stylish urban earrings feature pieces of primitive raw pyrite suspended from lengths of oxidized sterling silver chain.  Chain is securely attached to fabricated sterling silver ear wires which have been soldered closed.  Metal has been left oxidized to a beautiful rich charcoal gray patina which looks stunning with the metallic pyrite.

Pyrite chunks measure around 1/2" across at widest points and earrings hang a total of 3 3/8" from top of ear wires.

[E.671]

name: Bronze, Turquoise, Czech Glass & African Brass Dangle Earrings
description:
Exotic handwrought earrings crafted from beautiful bronze imprinted with one of my signature deep textures and paired with natural brown black turquoise, vintage green stone, earthy striped Czech artisan glass and primitive African brass beaded dangles.  Metal has been oxidized and steel brushed to a rich burnished sheen.  Stylish modern contemporary urban earrings with an ancient ethnic tribal vibe.

Earrings measure 3/4" across at widest point and hang a total of just under 3" from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wire to bottom of beaded dangle.

*The beautiful sheen of bronze can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[E.680]

name: Sterling Silver Teardrop & Quartz Point Dangle Earrings
description:
Long sterling silver dangle earrings crafted from hand forged and fabricated sterling teardrops embellished with gorgeous natural raw quartz crystal points.  Metal has been given a rustic primitive texture and then oxidized and steel brushed to a rich charcoal patina which contrasts beautifully with the sparkling crystals.  

Earrings measure 5/8" across at widest point and hang a total of 3 1/2" from top of hypoallergenic titanium ear wires to bottom of crystal dangles.

[E.670]

name: Quartz & Sterling Silver Teardrop Dangle Earrings
description:
Classic drop earrings with a contemporary urban edge, these earrings have been crafted from gorgeous faceted natural quartz paired with blackened sterling silver.  Beautiful clear quartz has lots of yellow inclusions and oxidized silver shows through as it passes through the quartz in a way that is quite intriguing.

Earrings measure 3/8" across at widest point and hang a total of 2 3/4" from top of soldered-closed sterling silver ear wires.

*These earrings can be ordered with regular steel brushed sterling silver if you prefer that look to the oxidized silver.  

[E.675]

name: Sterling Silver & Tigereye Earrings
description:
Simple, classic and stylish earrings crafted from beautiful honey caramel colored chatoyant tigereye cabochons set in handmade sterling silver bezels.  Traditional silversmith earrings compliment any attire from a formal business wardrobe to a T-shirt and jeans.

Earrings measure just under 5/8" across at widest point and hang a total of 1 1/4" from top of graceful forged sterling silver ear wires.

[E.687]

name: Raw Phantom Quartz & Sterling Silver Earrings
description:
Beautiful natural phantom quartz crystals in a lovely mix of clear, rust, brown and green on stylish forged sterling silver ear wires with skinny rustic primitive stick dangles.  Urban and stylish, yet earthy and organic.

Earrings measure just under 3/8" at widest point and hang a total of 2 5/8" from top of ear wires to bottom of dangles.

[E.679]

name: Copper Teardrop & Czech Glass Dangle Earrings
description:
Lovely feminine long dangle earrings crafted from hand forged and fabricated copper teardrops paired with gorgeous faceted Czech artisan glass in an luscious shade that could best be described as strawberry champagne.  Copper has been given a rustic primitive texture and a rich, dark hand-buffed patina that looks stunning with the color of the glass.  Modern contemporary urban metalsmith earrings with an exotic bohemian vibe.

Earrings measure 5/8" across at widest point of teardrop and hang a total of 3 1/4" from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wire to bottom of glass dangle.

[E.673]

name: Vintage Brass, Turquoise & Jasper Tribal Dangle Earrings
description:
Earthy dangle earrings crafted from salvaged pieces of rustic vintage Indian brass combined with brown black turquoise and celadon green jasper.  Pieces were hand-cut from a larger metalwork fragment, buffed smooth, and then oxidized and steel brushed to highlight beautiful primitive texture.  Stylish urban earrings with an ethnic tribal aesthetic.

Earrings measure approximately 1" at widest point and hang a total of approximately 3" from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wires.

These earrings will be handmade to order so please allow for slight variations.  Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

*The lovely sheen of brass can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[E.650]

name: Sterling Silver, Black Onyx, African Bauxite & Jasper Earrings
description:
Sterling silver earrings featuring beautiful large, high-polish black onyx cabochons beneath long, stylish ear wires stacked with rustic brick-colored African bauxite, black-and-white striped jasper, African brass and sterling silver coils.  Hip urban contemporary metalsmith earrings with a subtle ethnic tribal aesthetic.

Onyx cabochons are 5/8" in diameter and earrings hang a total of approximately 2" from top of forged sterling silver ear wires.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations.  Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Manasa Sterling Silver Snake Earrings
description:
Throughout history snakes have been symbols of rebirth and regeneration, immortality, fertility and wisdom. Manasa, the daughter of Lord Shiva, is the Hindu goddess of snakes. These stylish, sophisticated sterling silver snake earrings are a contemporary urban take on ancient folk mythology and symbolism.

Long, curvy snakes are opposite-facing and symmetrically curved and earrings hang a total of 3 1/2" from top of luxe forged sterling silver ear wires.

name: Sterling Silver Hoop Earrings I
description:
Fabulous, large sterling silver hoop earrings in one of my signature deep textures. Rows of smooth raised dots are steel brushed to shine against a more roughly textured oxidized background. Classic handwrought wide textural silversmith hoops are bold, striking and totally unique. Silver jewelry with a sophisticated urban look and an ever-so-slightly industrial vibe.

Earrings are 5/8" wide, approximately 1 1/4 - 1 1/2" in diameter and hang approximately 1 7/8" from top of titanium ear wires to bottom of hoop.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Sterling Silver Earrings
description:
Long ultra-textured sterling silver earrings in a tapered rectangle shape. These sculptural handwrought earrings are a labor of love, with each separate piece of wire cut to length and individually soldered on. Contemporary, stylish and urban with an ever-so-slightly industrial vibe.

Earrings are approximately 1/2" wide x 1 5/8" long and the total length is approximately 2" from tops of gracefully curving sterling silver ear wires. 

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Sterling Silver & Indonesian Glass Dangle Earrings
description:
Earthy, ethnic, rustic tribal long sterling silver dangle earrings.  Gorgeous multicolored Indonesian glass beads in shades of salmon, orange, red, mustard, green, black & white are stacked on long forged sterling silver wires with primitive forged and fabricated sterling silver stick dangles.

Earrings measure 5/16" at widest point and hang a total of just over 2 1/2" from top of ear wire to bottom of dangle.

[E.674]

name: Salvaged Antique Egyptian Brass Dangle Earrings
description:
Long exotic dangle earrings crafted from salvaged pieces of gorgeous antique Egyptian brass. These are cut from a larger piece which featured Arabic script created with traditional metalwork techniques of repousse and chasing. They are then buffed smooth, oxidized and steel brushed, and embellished with a fringe of 30 tiny handmade brass dangles - truly a labor of love! Stunning stylish urban artisan statement earrings with a bohemian ethnic tribal gypsy flair.

Earrings measure approximately 1" at widest point and hang a total of approximately 3" from top of hypoallergenic titanium ear wire to bottom of dangles.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for variations in the raised pattern on the metal. Your earrings will be "matched," they will be the same as each other, but they will be cut from different places in the Arabic script than the earrings in the photos. All of the script is equally beautiful. Please allow up to 5 days fabrication time.

*The beautiful sheen of brass can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[E.648]

name: Bronze Cuff Bracelet
description:
Gorgeous wide deeply textured bronze cuff bracelet. This cuff is distinctly urban and industrial while being tribal and ethnic at the same time. Oxidized and steel brushed to highlight unique hand-wrought pattern.

Cuff is 2" wide and a standard 6" long.

This bracelet will be made to order so please allow for ever-so-slight variations. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

*The beautiful satiny sheen of bronze can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[Due to its size, on international orders this item is shipped separately in its own box via USPS First Class Mail regardless of other purchases, which are automatically sent via USPS Priority Mail International. If you wish to save additional shipping costs and downgrade shipping on the other items which are automatically sent via USPS Priority Mail to First Class Mail, I can include them in this package and refund their shipping costs. name: Sterling Silver & White Moonstone Spiral Earrings
description:
Artsy sterling silver spiral earrings with beautiful luminous 8 mm white moonstone bezel set cabochons. Metal has been oxidized and steel brushed to contrast with the white moonstone and to accentuate the beautiful spiral pattern in these urban contemporary handwrought artisan metalsmith earrings.

Earrings measure 1" across and hang 1 5/8" from tops of forged sterling silver ear wires.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations. Please allow 5 days fabrication time.

name: Sterling Silver & Antique Bronze Buddha Sacred Amulet Talisman Necklace
description:
A gorgeous, detailed antique bronze Buddha that I have set in a hand fabricated sterling silver bezel and suspended from a substantial sterling silver link chain. Beautiful, serene and spiritual.

Buddha centerpiece is 1 1/4" wide x 2" tall and chain is about 18 1/2" long.

[N.025]

name: Russian Labradorite & Handwrought Sterling Silver Earrings
description:
Simple yet striking earrings crafted from gorgeous iridescent blue green Russian labradorite cabochons set in hand forged and fabricated sterling silver bezels.  Metal has been given a primitive organic texture and then oxidized and steel brushed.  Super stylish modern contemporary urban metalsmith earrings.

Labradorite cabochons are approximately 13 mm.  Earrings measure 11/16" in diameter and hang a total of 1 3/8" from top of luxe sterling silver ear wires.

[E.657]

name: Sterling Silver Earrings III
description:
Large textural handwrought sterling silver dangle earrings in a soft trapezoid shape. Substantial 22 gauge metal is embossed with a raised tribal pattern and then steel brushed to a rich charcoal gray patina. Modern contemporary silversmith earrings are urban and stylish with an exotic ethnic vibe.

Earrings measure just over 1" across at widest point and hang a total of just over 2" from top of soldered-closed sterling silver ear wires.

[E.661]

name: Sterling Silver Hoop Earrings II
description:
Beautiful large handwrought sterling silver hoop earrings with a rustic, primitive hand-stamped texture. Very ethnic and tribal. Metal has been oxidized and steel brushed to a satiny sheen.

Hoops are 3/8" wide, around 1 1/2 - 1 5/8" in diameter and hang a total of 1 3/4 - 2" from top of handmade titanium ear wires.

These earrings will be handmade to order so please allow for slight variations. Please allow up to 3 days fabrication time.

name: Salvaged Antique Silver Metalwork Artisan Earrings
description:
Fabulous earrings crafted from salvaged pieces of an antique European metalwork fragment depicting a highly detailed rural folk scene. I cut the pieces out, buffed the edges smooth, and soldered on long, graceful sterling silver ear wires.

At the risk of sounding immodest, it is impossible to describe how absolutely cool these earrings are! Urban, hip and stylish.

Earrings measure approximately 1 1/2" at widest point and hang a total of approximately 1 7/8" from top of forged sterling silver ear wires. Since the shape is a horizontal oval, I make the ear wires long so that the earrings hang just below the jawline for a very flattering effect. Silver plated brass is strong and rigid, yet light as a feather.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for ever so slight variations. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Vintage Brass Hoop Earrings: Turquoise Pyrite & Jasper Gemstone Dangle Hoops
description:
These earrings are crafted from vintage raw brass hoops from the 1970's that I believe were originally intended to be plated. I have given them a beautiful rich patina and added a dangle of organic earthy gemstones. Primitive African brass, deep brown blue green natural turquoise, cream beige jasper and shiny faceted pyrite look gorgeous with each other and with the rustic oxidized brass. These hoops are urban and sophisticated with a bohemian ethnic tribal vibe.

Patina on brass hoops has been sealed with Renaissance Wax and ear wires are hypoallergenic surgical steel.

Hoops are 1 1/4" in diameter and hang 2 1/2" from ear wire to bottom of dangle.


[E.612]

name: Hammered Bronze Hoop Earrings
description:
Super stylish large wide hammered bronze hoop earrings.  Classic texture has been wrought by hand with hundreds of hammer strikes.  Metal has then been oxidized and steel brushed to a rich golden sheen.  Modern contemporary urban earrings with a subtly exotic gypsy aesthetic.

Hoops are 5/8" wide, 1 3/8" in diameter and hang a total of just over 1 3/4" from top of hypoallergenic titanium ear wire.

*The beautiful sheen of bronze can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[E.663]

name: Seek Truth Copper & Glass Necklace
description:
Large hand fabricated copper bezel is hand-stamped on the inside with the words Seek Truth, using antique letter stamps, along with a variety of auspicious traditional Native American symbols.  It is then given a gorgeous verdigris patina and sealed with Renaissance Wax, and then set with a huge glass cabochon.  The outside of the necklace, including the solid copper chain, is then given a rich black patina.  This handwrought necklace, with its inspirational, spiritual, metaphysical aesthetic, is really one of my better inspirations  : )

Necklace centerpiece is 1 3/4" in diameter and chain length is about 18-20".

This necklace will be handmade to order so please allow for slight variations.  Please allow up to 5 days fabrication time.

name: Copper & White Agate Dangle Earrings
description:
Exotic large dangle earrings crafted from solid heavy-gauge copper that has been embossed with a raised pattern that is almost medieval in its aesthetic, and embellished with translucent white agate beaded dangles.  Metal has been oxidized and steel brushed to highlight striking pattern, and darkened copper makes for a beautiful contrast with white stones.  Unique stylish urban earrings with an ethnic tribal boho vibe.

Earrings measure 1 1/8" across at widest point and hang a total of 2 7/8" from top of luxe handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wires to bottom of beaded dangles.

*The beautiful rich sheen of copper can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[E.667]

name: Sterling Silver & Carnelian Dangle Earrings
description:
Super cool sterling silver dangle earrings crafted from gorgeous randomly faceted bright juicy orange carnelian and salvaged pieces of a vintage sterling necklace. Modern, contemporary urban artisan earrings are chic and stylish.

Earrings measure 5/8" across at widest point and hang a total of 2 1/4" from top of forged and fabricated sterling silver ear wire to bottom of dangle.

name: Bronze & Faceted Agate Teardrop Drop Earrings
description:
Feminine earthy classic drop earrings crafted from beautiful translucent faceted agate teardrops in shades of milky white, cocoa brown, deep brown and black, combined with matching white agate beads and suspended from lengths of bronze chain.  Modern contemporary urban artisan metalwork and gemstone earrings can be dressy or casual with a T-shirt and jeans.

Agate teardrops measure 3/8" across at widest point and earrings hang a total of just under 3 3/8" from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wires.

*The bronze chain can be kept glowing by rubbing it gently with fine steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.  

[E.665]

name: Salvaged Vintage Brass Wide Basket Hoop Earrings
description:
Cool ultra-wide basket hoop earrings crafted from salvaged pieces of gorgeous vintage brass with a beautiful rustic handwrought planished texture.  Earrings pieces were hand cut from a larger fragment, sanded and buffed smooth, and then forged into a generous wide hoop.  Metal was then oxdized and steel brushed to a lovely burnished golden sheen.  Hip, edgy and urban modern contemporary metalsmith hoops.

Hoops measure approximately 3/4 - 7/8" wide, 1" in diameter and hang a total of approximately 1 1/4" from top of handmade hypoallergenic titanium ear wires.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations.  Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

*The beautiful sheen of brass can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[E.658]

name: Sterling Silver & Carnelian Teardrop Dangle Earrings
description:
Lovely long dangle earrings crafted from hand forged and fabricated sterling silver paired with beautiful faceted carnelian teardrops in shades ranging from milky white to pale yellow orange. *Please note that the dangles go all wonky when they are laying flat in the photographs, but when they are worn the little spear-shaped dangles hang perfectly straight.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations. Yours will be cut from a different place in the larger metal fragment so please allow for slight variations in the exact pattern of the embossing, though they will be symmetrical with each other. All are equally beautiful. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Sterling Silver & Amethyst Dangle Earrings
description:
Large hammered hand forged sterling silver earrings in a pleasing teardrop shape embellished with gorgeous faceted purple amethyst beaded dangles. Beautiful feminine bohemian gypsy earrings.

Earrings measure 1 1/8" across and hang just over 2 1/4 from top of sterling silver ear wires to bottom of beaded dangles.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Sterling Silver Hoop Earrings IV
description:
Beautiful wide handwrought sterling silver hoop earrings embossed with one of my signature textures. Classic silversmith hoops with a modern contemporary look.

Earrings are 1/2" wide, 1 1/4" in diameter and hang a total of 1 5/8" from top of strong, hypoallergenic titanium ear wire to bottom of hoop.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations.  Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Copper Bangle Bracelet
description:
Rustic copper bangle bracelet forged from multiple interwoven layers of primitively textured heavy gauge solid copper that has been given a rich earthy black patina and hand-buffed to a satiny sheen. Blackened copper is edgy, sophisticated, stylish and urban with an ethnic, tribal vibe.

Flexible bracelet is around 2 1/2 in diameter..

This bracelet will be handmade to order via a very organic process, so please allow for slight variations. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Black Onyx & Sterling Silver Ring: Large Round Stone Adjustable Cocktail Ring
description:
Bodacious black onyx and sterling silver ring. Super chic and elegant contemporary urban cocktail ring. And that's beautiful downtown Brattleboro, Vermont reflected in the stone through my studio window : )

Large round onyx cabochon measures 1 3/16" in diameter. Shank is adjustable. 

[R.029]

name: Copper & Pyrite Chandelier Dangle Earrings
description:
Long ethnic tribal rustic dangle earrings fashioned from deeply textured copper, beautiful natural faceted metallic gray pyrite and earthy Czech glass.  Metal has been given a rich black patina and hand buffed to a lovely sheen.  Perfect for an exotic bohemian wardrobe or jeans and boots.  

Earrings measure 1" at widest point and hang a total of 2 7/8" from top of forged sterling silver ear wires to bottom of beaded dangles.

[E.524]

name: Titanium & Vintage Czech Glass Fiesta Hoops
description:
Fiesta Hoops:  Titanium & Vintage Czech Glass Beaded Hoops

Fun, colorful hoops crafted from gorgeous, rare vintage crayon colored Czech glass beads on handmade titanium ear wire.  Artsy urban boho hoops in beautiful shades of red, orange, yellow, green, blue and black.

Hoops are approximately 1 5/8" in diameter.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for ever-so-slight variations in the exact color patterns on the beads.  All of these fabulous beads are equally beautiful!

name: Copper & Raw Carnelian Drop Earrings
description:
Long dangle earrings crafted from beautiful raw burnt orange carnelian suspended from blackened solid copper double-link chain and embellished with solid copper beaded accents. An edgy and sophisticated take on the classic drop.

Earrings are around 1/2" at widest point and hang a total of 3 3/8" from top of hypoallergenic titanium ear wires.

*You will notice if you look carefully at some of the photos that the ear wire loop is not completely closed. Hurrying to take daylight photos before the sun went down (because that carnelian looks so spectacular with the light shining through it!), I neglected to close it all the way. That has now been corrected and both ear wires are closed to securely hold the chain : )

name: Hammered Sterling Silver Disc Earrings
description:
The classic hammered sterling disc.  Iconic.

Earrings are 1" in diameter and hang around 1 1/2" from top of luxe sterling silver ear wires.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Sterling Silver Hand-Stamped Artisan Hoops
description:
"Artisan Hoop" is the name I have given to earrings that are a hybrid of a substantial metalsmith earring and a hoop.  These sideways-facing artisan hoops have the same hand-stamped pattern on both sides so that there is no front side or back side, allowing them to be worn in either ear and be visible from all angles.  Modern contemporary urban earrings with an ethnic tribal vibe, these hoops are one of my signature designs and look fabulous on.

Earrings are 1 3/4" in diameter and hang approximately 2 1/8" from top of hypoallergenic titanium ear wires.

These earrings will be hand-made to order, so please allow for slight variations.  Please allow three days fabrication time.

*Please note that these earrings are not stamped sterling because I did not want to mar the texture, but they are sterling.

name: Copper Cuff Bracelet
description:
Beautiful wide deeply textured copper cuff bracelet. Oxidized and steel brushed to highlight unique hand-wrought pattern.

Cuff is 2" wide and a standard 6" long. The last photo shows the same bracelet in bronze just to give a sense of what it looks like on.

This bracelet will be made to order so please allow for ever-so-slight variations. Please allow up to 5 days fabrication time.

*The beautiful satiny sheen of copper can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

[Due to its size, on international orders this item is shipped separately in its own box via USPS First Class Mail regardless of other purchases, which are automatically sent via USPS Priority Mail International. If you wish to save additional shipping costs and downgrade shipping on the other items which are automatically sent via USPS Priority Mail to First Class Mail, I can include them in this package and refund their shipping costs. If you wish to consolidate shipping in this way, by downgrading to First Class on all items purchased, please contact me at the time of purchase.]

name: Sterling Silver, Coral, African Glass & Czech Glass Hoop Earrings
description:
Earthy and primitive tribal dangle earrings created from many wonderful treasures! Fabulous natural coral fangs in a pale coffee color hang along with rustic forged sterling silver stick dangles, multicolor Czech and African glass beaded dangles, and African brass beads on forged sterling silver hoops.

These front-facing, hoop-style earrings measure approximately 7/8" across and hang a total of approximately 2 1/2" from top of ear wires to bottom of dangles.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for variations in the exact size, shape and coloring of the coral pieces. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.

name: Blackened Copper Textural Bangle Bracelet
description:
Deeply textured handwrought thick copper bangle bracelet with a stylish pattern of raised dots. Hip, urban bracelet has a modern, contemporary ever-so-slightly industrial vibe while at the same time being rustic, ethnic and tribal. Oxidized and steel brushed blackened copper is a lovely color for a fall / autumn wardrobe or for any season.

Bracelet is 3/8" wide, circumference is around 8 1/8", and diameter is 2 5/8".

The beautiful sheen on the raised dots can be easily maintained by rubbing gently with steel wool and a piece will be included with your purchase.

name: Sterling Silver & Carnelian Earrings
description:
Classic handwrought sterling silver earrings set with big bright juicy orange carnelian cabochons. Modern contemporary minimalist design is timeless.

Earrings measure approximately 5/8 - 11/16" across and hang a total of approximately 1 1/8" from top of forged sterling silver ear wires. Carnelian cabochons are 12 mm.

These earrings will be made to order so please allow for slight variations. Please allow 3 days fabrication time.
